C++ based item modifier generator a la Borderlands or Terraria, creates statistical and behavioural modifiers for items in an RPG style. Can be used in anything from a Turn-Based RPG to shooter with RPG elements context.
How to:
Currently generates plain text output, can be ran in anything that can compile C++, when ran, you are prompted whether to use the default list of items or input your own, so far, there are two categories of items, equipables and weapons.
